text: Eugenia tekuensis is a species of plant in the family Myrtaceae. It is a tree endemic to Peninsular Malaysia, where it is known only from Pahang.Kochummen, K. M. 1998. Eugenia tekuensis. 2012 IUCN Red List of Threatened Species.
